<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV106">
<l>kaṟuttetirnta kālanēmi kālaṉōṭu kūṭavaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṟuttavāḻi caṅkutaṇṭu villumvāḷu mēntiṉāy</l>
<l>toṟukkalanta vūṉamaḵto ḻikkavaṉṟu kuṉṟamuṉ</l>
<l>poṟuttaniṉpu kaḻkalālor nēcamillai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who bear a discus, a conch, a staff, a bow, and a sword</l>
<l>That severed on that day [the head] of Kālanemi who became angry and attacked</l>
<l rend="indent">In such a way that [he] joined Death!</l>
<l>Except for Your glory—of You who previously bore the hill on that day in order to</l>
<l>Destroy the evil that befell the herd of cows—</l>
<l rend="indent">my heart does not have an[other] attachment!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
